  "keyFeatures": [
    "SDK-style SQL projects with MSBuild support (Microsoft.Build.Sql)",
    "Cross-platform CLI for dacpac/bacpac packaging and deployment (SqlPackage)",
    "Database schema portability across SQL Server versions and Azure SQL environments",
    "Declarative database development with T-SQL stored as source code",
    "Database references and NuGet package references for multi-database projects",
    "SQLCMD variable substitution for environment-specific deployments",
    "Pre/post-deployment scripts for data seeding and migrations",
    "T-SQL code analysis with custom rules support",
    "System dacpac packages for master, msdb, Azure SQL, Synapse, and Fabric",
    "ScriptDOM T-SQL parser library"
  ],
