    "Microsoft.SqlServer.TransactSql.ScriptDom (T-SQL parser API)",
    "ArtifactReference (dacpac database reference in .sqlproj)",
    "PackageReference (NuGet dacpac reference in .sqlproj)",
    "SqlCmdVariable (variable definition in .sqlproj)",
    "PreDeploy / PostDeploy (script items in .sqlproj)",
    "DSP (target platform property in .sqlproj)"
